      <title>全球极端天气可能导致食品价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/wheat-coffee-sugar-other-food-prices-are-rising-due-to-bad-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从亚洲到美洲的干旱、暴雨和火灾引发了人们对农作物收成的担忧，推高了主食价格，最终可能导致食品杂货账单上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/wheat-coffee-sugar-other-food-prices-are-rising-due-to-bad-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 07:28:19 GMT</pubDate>
